# ACF JSON Field Format

## Block JSON Structure

Each block has a `.json` file defining its ACF field group:

```json
{
	"title": "Block Name",
	"fields": [
		{
			"key": "field_{slug}_block_options",
			"label": "Block Name",
			"type": "accordion",
			"open": 1,
			"multi_expand": 1
		},
		{
			"key": "field_{slug}_data_tab",
			"label": "Data",
			"type": "tab"
		},
		{
			"key": "field_{slug}_heading",
			"label": "Heading",
			"name": "heading",
			"type": "text"
		}
	]
}
```

## Key Convention

Always prefix with `field_{block_slug}_`:

```json
{ "key": "field_main_hero_heading", "name": "heading", "type": "text" }
```

For sub*fields in repeaters: `field*{slug}_{repeater}_{field}`:

```json
{ "key": "field_main_hero_items_title", "name": "title", "type": "text" }
```

## Auto-Injected Fields (DO NOT add to JSON)

These are added automatically at block registration:

- **Settings tab** with display on/off (button_group)
- **Spacing group** (top/bottom: small/medium/large/xlarge/custom/none)
- **Custom CSS** (textarea)
- **Custom Classes** (text)
- **Unique ID** (text)

## Block Optional Settings (top-level)

```json
{
    "title": "Block Name",
    "active": false,
    "settings": {
        "category": "uncategorized",
        "icon": "layout",
        "post_types": ["page", "post"]
    },
    "fields": [...]
}
```

- `active: false` → disables the block
- `post_types` → defaults to `["page"]` if not specified

## Common Field Types (JSON format)

### Image (ALWAYS return ID, preview w200)

```json
{
	"key": "field_{slug}_image",
	"label": "Image",
	"name": "image",
	"type": "image",
	"return_format": "id",
	"preview_size": "w200"
}
```

### Link

```json
{
	"key": "field_{slug}_link",
	"label": "Link",
	"name": "link",
	"type": "link",
	"return_format": "array"
}
```

### Select

```json
{
	"key": "field_{slug}_style",
	"label": "Style",
	"name": "style",
	"type": "select",
	"choices": {
		"default": "Default",
		"alternate": "Alternate"
	},
	"default_value": "default"
}
```

### Button Group

```json
{
	"key": "field_{slug}_layout",
	"label": "Layout",
	"name": "layout",
	"type": "button_group",
	"choices": {
		"left": "Left",
		"center": "Center",
		"right": "Right"
	},
	"default_value": "left"
}
```

### Textarea

```json
{
	"key": "field_{slug}_heading",
	"label": "Heading",
	"name": "heading",
	"type": "textarea",
	"rows": 2,
	"new_lines": "br",
	"instructions": "Line breaks are preserved"
}
```

### Repeater

```json
{
	"key": "field_{slug}_items",
	"label": "Items",
	"name": "items",
	"type": "repeater",
	"min": 1,
	"max": 6,
	"layout": "block",
	"button_label": "Add {item}",
	"collapsed": "field_{slug}_items_title",
	"sub_fields": [
		{
			"key": "field_{slug}_items_title",
			"label": "Title",
			"name": "title",
			"type": "text"
		},
		{
			"key": "field_{slug}_items_image",
			"label": "Image",
			"name": "image",
			"type": "image",
			"return_format": "id",
			"preview_size": "w200"
		}
	]
}
```

### Group

```json
{
	"key": "field_{slug}_cta",
	"label": "CTA",
	"name": "cta",
	"type": "group",
	"layout": "block",
	"sub_fields": [
		{
			"key": "field_{slug}_cta_heading",
			"label": "Heading",
			"name": "heading",
			"type": "text"
		}
	]
}
```

### WYSIWYG

```json
{
	"key": "field_{slug}_content",
	"label": "Content",
	"name": "content",
	"type": "wysiwyg",
	"tabs": "all",
	"toolbar": "full",
	"media_upload": 0,
	"delay": 1
}
```

### Number

```json
{
	"key": "field_{slug}_count",
	"label": "Count",
	"name": "count",
	"type": "number",
	"default_value": 3,
	"min": 1,
	"max": 12
}
```

### True/False

```json
{
	"key": "field_{slug}_show_title",
	"label": "Show Title",
	"name": "show_title",
	"type": "true_false",
	"default_value": 1
}
```

### oEmbed (Video)

```json
{
	"key": "field_{slug}_video",
	"label": "Video",
	"name": "video",
	"type": "oembed"
}
```

### Post Object

```json
{
	"key": "field_{slug}_post",
	"label": "Post",
	"name": "post",
	"type": "post_object",
	"post_type": ["post"],
	"return_format": "id",
	"multiple": 0
}
```

### Relationship

```json
{
	"key": "field_{slug}_posts",
	"label": "Posts",
	"name": "posts",
	"type": "relationship",
	"post_type": ["post"],
	"return_format": "id",
	"min": 1,
	"max": 6
}
```

### Tab

```json
{
	"key": "field_{slug}_content_tab",
	"label": "Content",
	"type": "tab"
}
```

### Conditional Logic

```json
{
	"key": "field_{slug}_custom_text",
	"label": "Custom Text",
	"name": "custom_text",
	"type": "text",
	"conditional_logic": [
		[
			{
				"field": "field_{slug}_style",
				"operator": "==",
				"value": "custom"
			}
		]
	]
}
```
